name: SFSafariPageProperties
desc: An object that captures information about a webpage.

items.name: var isActive: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the page is currently active.

items.name: var url: URL?
items.desc: Indicates the URL of the page.

items.name: var usesPrivateBrowsing: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the page is using Safari Private Browsing.
